schemas.name: Query.graphql
schemas.content:
# Here's all the field types you can use in your query!
type Query {
  # My Name
  name: String
  # My Email
  email: String
  # My current employer
  company: String
  # My Twitter
  twitter: String
  # My GitHub
  github: String
  # My LinkedIn
  linkedin: String
  # Am I employed?
  employed: Boolean
  jobs: [Job]
  repos: [Repo]
  talks: [Talk]
  projects: [Project]
  education: [Education]
}

# https://github.com/1andee/portfolio/blob/b990a08008485fe40cf69b5f782e474c480a8489/src/server/types/Query.graphql:
# Here's all the field types you can use in your query!
type Query {
  # My Name
  name: String
  # My Email
  email: String
  # My current employer
  company: String
  # My Twitter
  twitter: String
  # My GitHub
  github: String
  # My LinkedIn
  linkedin: String
  # Am I employed?
  employed: Boolean
  jobs: [Job]
  repos: [Repo]
  talks: [Talk]
  projects: [Project]
  education: [Education]
}

# https://github.com/1andee/portfolio/blob/3955720773102ef1140b75db78eca3a088feb098/src/server/types/Job.graphql:
type Job {
  # Company name
  company: String
  # Title
  title: String
  # Where this job was located
  location: String
  # Start date
  started: String
  # End date
  finished: String
}

# https://github.com/1andee/portfolio/blob/3955720773102ef1140b75db78eca3a088feb098/src/server/types/Repo.graphql:
type Repo {
  # Repo Name
  name: String
  # Link to repo
  url: String
  # Repo description
  description: String
  # Programming language
  language: String
  # Number of stars
  stars: Int
  # Is it forked?
  fork: Boolean
  # Owner of the repo
  owner: String
}

# https://github.com/1andee/portfolio/blob/3955720773102ef1140b75db78eca3a088feb098/src/server/types/Talk.graphql:
type Talk {
  # Talk name
  name: String
  # Event that hosted this talk
  event: String
  # Date
  date: String
  # Video link
  video: String
  # Slides link
  slides: String
  # Completed?
  done: Boolean,
  # Location
  location: String
}

# https://github.com/1andee/portfolio/blob/3955720773102ef1140b75db78eca3a088feb098/src/server/types/Project.graphql:
type Project {
  # Project name
  name: String
  # Program description
  description: String
  # Repository URL
  github: String
  # Website (if deployed)
  website: String
}

# https://github.com/1andee/portfolio/blob/3955720773102ef1140b75db78eca3a088feb098/src/server/types/Education.graphql:
type Education {
  # Institution name
  school: String
  # Program name
  program: String
  # Start date
  started: String
  # End date
  finished: String
}
